Package: conquer
Type: Package
Title: Convolution-type smoothed quantile regression
Version: 1.0
Date: 2020-03-06
Author: Xiaoou Pan, Kean Ming Tan, Wen-Xin Zhou
Maintainer: Xiaoou Pan <xip024@ucsd.edu>
Description: Fast and accurate convolution-type smoothed quantile regression (conquer) implemented via Barzilai-Borwein gradient descent with a Huber warm start.
             Statistical inference via multiplier bootstrap for conquer is also included.
Depends: R (>= 3.6.0)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
SystemRequirements: C++11
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.3), matrixStats, stats
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
